## V0.2.2 formats

sunlight_hours.txt (Text format)

```txt
2024-12-15 23:59:59:
```

lux_readings.csv (CSV format)

```csv
timestamp,lux
2024-12-15 08:30:45,1234.56
2024-12-15 08:31:15,1543.21
```
